The Griffin household includes two teenagers, a cynical dog who is smarter than everyone else,
and a mutant baby who makes numerous attempts to eradicate his parents and siblings. Heading up
this eclectic household is Peter Griffin. Peter does his best to do what\\\&#039;s right for the family,
but along the way, he makes mistakes that are the stuff of legends.
